1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,557
Most traders don't lose money on bad charts. They lose it buying euphoria, and selling fear.

2
00:00:05,557 --> 00:00:12,020
Euphoria is an AI platform for BNB Chain that measures the emotion driving the market — not just the price.

3
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:14,759
Ask it about any token, and five agents go to work.

4
00:00:14,759 --> 00:00:18,380
Scout reads the data; Narrative explains why it's moving.

5
00:00:18,380 --> 00:00:22,381
Crowd scores the FOMO while Reverse argues the contrarian case.

6
00:00:22,381 --> 00:00:29,559
Then the Judge delivers a verdict — buy, sell, or watch — with full reasoning, every signal traced to its source.

7
00:00:29,059 --> 00:00:34,688
And it's not just talk — we turned that thesis into a deterministic, backtestable strategy.

8
00:00:34,688 --> 00:00:38,956
Ride momentum, move to cash when the crowd turns euphoric or fearful.

9
00:00:38,956 --> 00:00:44,091
On Bitcoin it beat buy & hold through a 30% crash, with a fraction of the drawdown.

10
00:00:43,590 --> 00:00:46,446
The edge holds across the BNB ecosystem.

11
00:00:46,446 --> 00:00:52,944
On PancakeSwap's CAKE and BNB itself, Euphoria preserved capital while buy & hold bled out.

12
00:00:52,444 --> 00:00:57,189
Pure, reproducible, and unit-tested — powered by CoinMarketCap.

13
00:00:57,189 --> 00:01:02,009
Euphoria. Trade market emotions, not charts. Built for BNB Hack.

